ours at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC using a time-weighted average of the perpetual-spot price difference. The exchange applies a ±0.1% dampener to reduce funding volatility, with rates typically ranging from -2% to +2% daily. Funding payments occur automatically between long and short position holders, with no additional fees beyond the standard 0.05% taker rate."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
